pipeline itself is healthy with no blockers. I'm going to stay silent and not report anything. I'm settling on the most recent state snapshot from the cron:6f3323ef report at 00:32 UTC as my baseline for comparison."},{"type":"text","text":"Comparing current state (00:41 UTC) against last known state (00:14 UTC / 00:32 UTC):\n\n- All 3 cron sessions still running ✅ — no change\n- telegram:direct:6053576134 ended ~22:02 UTC — noted in prior report, not new\n- No new failures, blockers, or sessions spawned\n- Pipeline: HEALTHY\n\n**Silent. No material changes. Exiting quietly.**"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":427,"output":537,"totalTokens":44884,"cacheRead":14272,"cacheWrite":29648,"cost":{"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776213706978,"responseId":"062e11ccb4b06fdbb9e91a742de48dd3","__openclaw":{"id":"f02beb26","seq":7}}]},{"key":"agent:master-orchestrator:main","kind":"other","channel":"webchat","origin":{"provider":"heartbeat"},"displayName":"webchat:g-agent-master-orchestrator-main","deliveryContext":{"channel":"webchat","to":"heartbeat"},"updatedAt":1776211905515,"sessionId":"bca9bbb9-d1eb-408d-9e3d-14dd521dcc45","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","contextTokens":200000,"totalTokens":101430,"estimatedCostUsd":0,"status":"done","startedAt":1776211871811,"endedAt":1776211903761,"runtimeMs":31950,"systemSent":true,"abortedLastRun":false,"lastChannel":"webchat","lastTo":"heartbeat","transcriptPath":"/root/.openclaw/agents/master-orchestrator/sessions/bca9bbb9-d1eb-408d-9e3d-14dd521dcc45.jsonl","messages":[{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Night time (UTC+7: 07:11 AM actually, wait...). Current time is 00:11 UTC = 07:11 AM UTC+7. That's not within the 23:00-07:00 night silence window. But per HEARTBEAT.md: \"Night time 23:00–07:00 UTC+7 → Stay silent unless critical\". 07:11 AM UTC+7 is past the silence window. Let me check sessions.\n\nActually wait, the night silence is 23:00-07:00 UTC+7. Current UTC is 00:11 UTC = 07:11 AM UTC+7. \n\nSo the window has closed—it's past 07:00 UTC+7 now, which means I should be sending reports instead of staying silent. Let me check the active sessions."},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_scba5uxifnnk_1","name":"sessions_list","arguments":{"limit":5,"activeMinutes":10,"messageLimit":0}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":2102,"output":220,"totalTokens":99552,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":97230,"cost":{"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776211871958,"responseId":"062e0aa2ef32e6ae724060849e3f6844","__openclaw":{"id":"ab3104b0","seq":151}},{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Only 2 cron sessions running (e7885813 and 6f3323ef) and the 5p QLHV cron (ed2d0b5d) also running. No active Telegram group sessions. No new failures. Pipeline is healthy. The morning silence window (23:00-07:00 UTC+7) is over (it's now 07:11 AM UTC+7). However, there are no meaningful changes to report and the pipeline is stable. The system was silent overnight correctly. I should stay silent since nothing has changed materially."},{"type":"text","text":"\nHEARTBEAT_OK"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":1975,"output":125,"totalTokens":101555,"cacheRead":97170,"cacheWrite":2285,"cost":{"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776211884831,"responseId":"062e0aba05e65ceda96023c45c2be25b","__openclaw":{"id":"2adbd823","seq":153}}]},{"key":"agent:master-orchestrator:cron:53c5832a-eecc-4d6b-a4c3-d1b78a430dca","kind":"other","channel":"unknown","label":"Cron: Daily Briefing 5AM UTC+7","displayName":"Cron: Daily Briefing 5AM UTC+7","updatedAt":1776208566543,"sessionId":"26f7c499-7fac-499e-bf9f-921a2e2ab1b6","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","contextTokens":200000,"totalTokens":21354,"estimatedCostUsd":0,"systemSent":true,"transcriptPath":"/root/.openclaw/agents/master-orchestrator/ses